[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1370","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1370.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1160","title":"HP-UX ftpd/kftpd 权限许可和访问控制漏洞","description":"HP-UX 10.x 和 9.x 系统中的 ftpd/kftpd 服务存在权限许可和访问控制漏洞，由于对用户权限验证不充分，本地攻击者可利用该漏洞绕过权限检查获取 root 权限，特定条件下远程攻击者也可能利用此漏洞提升权限。该漏洞影响 HP-UX 多个版本，危害等级严重，CVSS 评分 10.0。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1160"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-02-02T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:50.913","remediation":"根据 HP 安全公告 HPSBUX9702-055，HP-UX 9.X 系统安装补丁 PHNE_10008，HP-UX 10.0X/10.10 安装 PHNE_10009，HP-UX 10.20 安装 PHNE_10010，kftpd 用户安装 PHNE_10011。如版本已停止支持无法获取补丁，应立即在 /etc/ftpd/ftpusers 中禁止匿名用户登录，并限制 ftp 用户目录权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/h-33.shtml","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167420581&w=2","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7437.php","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1160.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1160","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1160.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d0a8c476da89b37a2bbb6193b7964b10d03aff75/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1160.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mm2m-w84p-r249/GHSA-mm2m-w84p-r249.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87949/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1160.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154300_154400.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000144.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--21e53856-a55b-418e-a012-abc3ae0a69bc.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1370.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1221","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1221.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0959","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9144,\"outputTokens\":24,\"totalTokens\":10832}}","description":"SGI IRIX 6.4 系统中的 startmidi 程序存在符号链接漏洞。该程序在创建或写入临时文件时未对文件路径进行充分校验，本地攻击者可通过创建指向系统任意敏感文件的符号链接，诱使程序跟随链接并修改目标文件内容。由于 startmidi 以较高权限运行，攻击者可利用此漏洞篡改关键系统文件（如密码文件、配置文件和可执行程序），从而实现本地权限提升至 root。该漏洞仅需本地登录权限即可利用，无需额外身份认证，影响所有运行 SGI IRIX 6.4 且默认安装 startmidi 程序的系统。SGI 已在 1998 年安全公告中发布补丁修复此问题。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0959"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:24.607","remediation":"SGI IRIX 6.4 的 startmidi 程序存在符号链接（symlink）攻击漏洞（CVE-1999-0959，公告编号 19980301-01-PX），本地低权限用户可通过竞争条件在 /tmp 等临时目录中创建指向敏感系统文件（如 /etc/passwd、/etc/shadow）的符号链接，当 root 用户执行 startmidi 时，程序会跟随该链接并修改目标文件，导致任意文件篡改或权限提升。建议立即从 SGI 官方补丁服务器 ftp://patches.sgi.com/support/free/security/advisories/19980301-01-PX 下载并安装编号为 19980301-01-PX 的安全补丁，该补丁修复了 startmidi 程序中不安全的临时文件创建逻辑，使其在创建临时文件时使用 O_EXCL 标志并配合安全的临时目录机制，避免符号链接跟随。若无法立即安装补丁，临时缓解措施包括：以 root 身份执行 chmod 755 /usr/sbin/startmidi 并移除 setuid/setgid 位（chmod 755 已隐含移除），或通过文件系统挂载选项将 /tmp 设置为 nosuid、nodev、noexec，以及使用临时 ACL 或 cron 任务定期清理 /tmp 中不属于合法用户的符号链接。长期建议将系统升级至 SGI IRIX 6.5.22 或更高版本，该版本已包含对所有已知 startmidi 及同类 symlink 漏洞的完整修复。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/8447","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/469","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1634","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19355","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/184a5a0fb7dfcbb1c5bcfd5178078c78dc1e4738/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0959.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0959","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0959.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/95eeda559fd899397df50f658cf25cf01bb1e4ea/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0959.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8b1565557a8e0fb04634f0989d7e7dd7febd4847/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-8xqm-h8vp-397q/GHSA-8xqm-h8vp-397q.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154300_154400.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_0.list.dict","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0959.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--864d9a7d-62f2-442b-be2f-b0a90d45a2b5.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1221.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0516","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0516.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0309","title":"HP HP-UX vgdisplay 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"HP-UX 操作系统的 vgdisplay 程序中存在权限分配不当漏洞。本地攻击者可利用该程序以普通用户身份执行 vgdisplay 命令，由于程序未正确限制访问权限，导致攻击者获得 root 级别的系统权限，从而完全控制受影响系统。该漏洞影响 HP-UX 多个版本，需要本地用户账户作为攻击条件。CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0309"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:07.363","remediation":"立即安装 HP 安全公告 HPSBUX9702-056 中对应的补丁（适用于 HP-UX 10.x 系列）。如无法立即打补丁，可通过 chmod u-s /usr/sbin/vgdisplay 移除 vgdisplay 的 setuid 权限位作为临时缓解措施；同时限制可登录系统的本地用户范围，仅授予可信用户访问权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9702-056"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0516.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0347","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0347.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0174","title":"SGI Skunkware 2.0 view-source CGI 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Skunkware 2.0 的 view-source CGI 程序存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标发送包含 `..`（点点）序列的特制 HTTP 请求，绕过路径限制读取服务器上的任意文件。该漏洞无需身份认证即可利用，可导致敏感信息泄露，影响 Skunkware 2.0 版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0174"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:45.550","remediation":"立即停止并移除 /cgi-bin/view-source CGI 脚本；如业务需要该功能，重写脚本并对路径参数做严格的输入过滤，拒绝包含 \"../\"、绝对路径或特殊字符的请求；同时在 Web 服务器层面（Apache/Nginx）配置 `AllowOverride None` 和 `Options -Indexes`，并添加访问控制规则阻止对 CGI 目录的未授权访问。由于 Skunkware 2.0 已停止维护多年，建议迁移至较新的操作系统发行版及标准 Web 服务器软件包。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0174","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20568","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0174.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea60fdb4a03411be38d3e381b26e4c4/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0174.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0174","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0174.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0174.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0174.md","https://github.com/decal/werdlists/blob/81edb463f7f6311c85defefaf75ac9cd58e5cfb9/exploit-info/symantec-attack-signatures.txt","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mfjc-659f-pj9j/GHSA-mfjc-659f-pj9j.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/web-cgi.rules","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0347.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0607","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0607.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0369","title":"Sun Solaris 7.0 sdtcm_convert 本地缓冲区溢出权限提升漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris 7.0 系统中 OpenWindows 环境下的 sdtcm_convert 日历转换工具存在栈缓冲区溢出漏洞。攻击者通过向该 setuid 程序传递特制的命令行参数，可触发缓冲区溢出，覆盖返回地址，从而以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞需要本地访问权限，无需用户交互即可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0369"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"1997-02-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"应用 Sun 安全公告 #183 提供的补丁，或升级到已修复该漏洞的 Solaris 版本。由于 Solaris 7.0 已停止支持，建议迁移到受支持的 Solaris 版本或替代操作系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T13:56:22.329038950+00:00","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/183"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0607.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0129","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0129.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0047","title":"Sendmail MIME转换缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"sendmail 8.8.3 及 8.8.4 版本在处理 MIME 邮件编码转换时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标邮件服务器发送特制的 MIME 邮件触发该漏洞，导致缓冲区越界写入，可能造成服务崩溃或任意代码执行。该漏洞影响广泛部署的 sendmail 邮件传输代理，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0047"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-01-28T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:27.130","remediation":"升级 sendmail 至 8.8.5 或更高版本，该版本已修复 MIME 转换中的缓冲区溢出问题。若无法立即升级，可在 sendmail.cf 中禁用 MIME 转换功能（O MimeVersion=0）或限制邮件大小作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/685"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0129.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1251","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1251.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0966","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":10771,\"outputTokens\":21,\"totalTokens\":10792}}","description":"CVE-1999-0966 是 Solaris 系统中 libc 库的 getopt 函数存在的本地缓冲区溢出漏洞。由于 getopt 在处理命令行参数 argv[0] 时未对输入长度进行边界校验，本地用户可构造超长 argv[0] 参数触发缓冲区溢出，进而覆盖相邻内存并提升权限至 root。该漏洞影响运行 Solaris 操作系统的本地账户，攻击条件为攻击者需拥有目标系统的本地登录权限，利用方式是通过执行特制程序使溢出覆盖返回地址或环境变量以实现本地提权。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0966"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-01-27T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:25.483","remediation":"建议升级到 Sun 已发布修复该 libc getopt 缓冲区溢出补丁的 Solaris 版本（如 Solaris 2.6 的 105755 补丁簇或 Solaris 7 的 108116 补丁簇）。如无法立即打补丁，应限制普通用户对受影响 setuid root 程序的执行权限，并定期审查系统中 setuid 文件以降低本地提权风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0966"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1251.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0130","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0130.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0048","title":"Unix Talkd 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Talk 服务守护进程（talkd）在处理 DNS 响应信息时存在输入验证缺陷，当攻击者向目标系统提供特制的恶意 DNS 数据时，可导致缓冲区溢出或命令注入，从而以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响多种 UNIX 变种系统（包括 AIX、HP-UX、Solaris 等），攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，危害等级严重。厂商已发布安全补丁修复此漏洞。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0048"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-01-27T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:27.283","remediation":"建议立即禁用 talkd 服务（在 inetd.conf 或 xinetd.d 中注释掉 talk 条目并重启服务），如必须使用应升级至修复该漏洞的版本。同时在边界防火墙上屏蔽 UDP 端口 517（talkd 默认端口），限制对 talk 服务的网络访问权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/147"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0130.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0194","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0194.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0081","title":"wu-ftpd RNFR 命令文件覆盖漏洞","description":"wu-ftpd FTP 服务器在实现 FTP 重命名功能时存在路径验证缺陷，未经认证的远程攻击者可通过 FTP 协议发送特制的 RNFR（重命名来源）与 RNTO（重命名为）命令序列，将服务器上的任意文件重写为指定目标文件名，导致文件被覆盖或篡改。该漏洞影响早期版本的 wu-ftpd FTP 服务器，攻击者无需登录认证即可利用匿名 FTP 会话执行操作，成功利用可覆盖系统配置文件或可执行文件，进而可能导致服务异常中断或权限提升。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0081"],"sources":["cve","epss"],"published":"1997-01-11T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:32.170","remediation":"wu-ftpd 已停止维护多年，建议立即迁移至 vsftpd、ProFTPD 或 Pure-FTPd 等活跃维护的 FTP 服务器软件。迁移前，在 /etc/hosts.allow 和防火墙层面限制 FTP 服务仅对可信 IP 段开放，并禁用匿名用户写入权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0081","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0081"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0194.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0131","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0131.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0049","title":"SGI IRIX Csetup 任意文件创建或覆盖漏洞","description":"IRIX 操作系统中的 Csetup 工具存在任意文件创建或覆写漏洞，由于未对用户输入的文件路径进行充分校验，具有本地访问权限的攻击者可利用该漏洞创建或覆盖系统关键文件，从而提升权限或导致系统崩溃。该漏洞影响 SGI IRIX 多个版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。建议用户升级至不受影响的版本或应用厂商提供的安全补丁。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0049"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-01-08T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:27.417","remediation":"将 IRIX 升级至 6.3 或更高版本；若无法升级，立即移除 Csetup 的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /usr/sbin/Csetup），并限制不可信用户的本地登录权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0049"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0131.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1473","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1473.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1311","title":"HP HP-UX dtlogin/dtsession 安全绕过漏洞","description":"HP-UX 操作系统的 dtlogin 和 dtsession 组件存在安全绕过漏洞。本地攻击者可通过利用该漏洞绕过身份认证机制，获取系统未授权的访问权限并提升至更高权限。该漏洞影响 HP-UX 10.10 和 10.20 版本，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。建议用户及时升级系统或应用厂商发布的安全补丁以修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1311"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-01-07T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:10.170","remediation":"立即安装 HP 安全公告 HPSBUX9701-055 中提供的对应补丁。对于 HP-UX 10.10 系统，安装 dtlogin/dtsession 安全补丁 PHSS_10666；对于 HP-UX 10.20 系统，安装补丁 PHSS_10667。如系统已停止维护无法获取补丁，应限制本地用户对 dtlogin 和 dtsession 二进制文件的执行权限，或升级至受支持的 HP-UX 11i 版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/h-21.shtml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e8d44fc9434dcaf08511a3267e0bf049a6756de/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1311.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1311","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1311.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f9199c6ea2112c9d2536a126688b640a45f0982a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1311.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f37077e857e7a28bab83d284c23299407fb1af7e/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7p86-2vjq-95x7/GHSA-7p86-2vjq-95x7.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154300_154400.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1311.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000138.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--2d67cc55-7202-466b-80fb-3bde032b6d61.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idbypass"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1473.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1424","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1424.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1249","title":"HP HP-UX movemail 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"HP-UX 10.20 系统自带的 movemail 程序存在不安全的文件权限配置，导致本地用户可利用该缺陷进行权限提升攻击。由于 movemail 以特权身份运行或权限设置不当，攻击者可在获得本地低权限访问后，通过直接执行或利用该程序执行恶意操作，从而获取系统更高级别的控制权限。该漏洞影响 HP-UX 10.20 版本，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1249"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-01-06T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:02.157","remediation":"建议立即应用 HP 安全公告 HPSBUX9701-047 提供的补丁程序。如无法安装补丁，可手动执行 `chmod 755 /usr/bin/movemail` 移除 movemail 二进制文件的 setuid/setgid 权限位，以消除本地用户利用不安全权限进行提权的风险。长期修复方案为升级至 HP-UX 11.x 或更高版本，这些版本已修复该安全问题。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.codetalker.com/advisories/vendor/hp/hpsbux9701-047.html","http://www.osvdb.org/8099","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2057"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1424.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0136","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0136.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0051","title":"SGI IRIX FLEXlm LicenseManager 任意文件创建与远程代码执行漏洞","description":"FLEXlm LicenseManager（lmgrd）许可管理守护进程 4.0 至 5.0 版本存在文件创建与程序执行漏洞。该漏洞源于 FLEXlm 对用户提交的请求未进行充分校验，导致本地攻击者可利用 lmgrd 进程的权限创建任意文件或执行恶意程序，进而获取目标系统的完全控制权。该漏洞影响 SGI IRIX 及 Sun Solaris 等多个 Unix 平台，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。厂商已发布安全更新修复此问题，建议用户升级至最新版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0051"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-01-06T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:27.673","remediation":"升级 FLEXlm License Manager 至 5.0 以上版本，或禁用 License Manager 服务。在无法升级的环境下，通过防火墙限制对 lmgrd 端口 (TCP/UDP 27000-27009) 的访问，仅允许受信客户端连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0051","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19350","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0051.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0051","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0051.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0051.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0051.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-68w9-8p8f-9gr8/GHSA-68w9-8p8f-9gr8.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_4.list.dict","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154200_154300.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0051.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0136.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0136.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0136.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1242","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1242.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1120","title":"SGI IRIX netprint 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 6.4 及更早版本中的 netprint 工具在调用 disable 程序时信任 PATH 环境变量，未使用绝对路径或进行路径校验。本地攻击者可修改 PATH 环境变量，将恶意程序置于优先搜索路径中，从而诱使 netprint 以提升的权限执行任意代码，实现本地权限提升。该漏洞影响 SGI IRIX 6.4 及之前版本，需本地访问权限，CVSS 评分 4.6。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1120"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-01-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:45.770","remediation":"升级 SGI IRIX 至 6.5 或更高版本，该版本已修复 netprint 对 PATH 环境变量的信任问题。如无法升级，可移除 netprint 的 setuid 位（chmod u-s /usr/lib/netprint）并限制可执行用户组，同时确保 disable 程序路径使用绝对路径而非依赖 PATH 环境变量。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167420403&w=2","http://www.osvdb.org/993","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/395","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2107","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19313","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/712a40967986b700313860b08048435be4fa9839/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1120.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1120","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1120.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/248c2167e720df96125f6ac9925793063a207510/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1120.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-83rr-9jf8-f8mr/GHSA-83rr-9jf8-f8mr.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_800_900.json","https://github.com/Team-Atlanta/aixcc-asc-atlantis/blob/785c446f980e12155935db586aa30c3b54adcc86/crs/src/crs-patch/smith/smith/lib/cwe/raw/CWE-426.txt","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_2.list.dict","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--744f1f3c-c086-49c3-93d2-dafae56a0c3a.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1120.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1242.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0849","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0849.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0582","title":"Microsoft Windows NT/2000 账户锁定策略配置不当漏洞","description":"Windows NT 和 Windows 2000 系统的账户锁定策略存在安全配置不当漏洞，默认情况下账户锁定阈值、锁定持续时间及锁定计数器重置时间等关键参数未设置或设置不合理，导致远程攻击者可对用户账户进行暴力破解或字典攻击，无需触发账户锁定机制即可持续尝试登录。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及 Windows 2000 系统，攻击者只需通过网络可达即可利用，无需任何身份认证。建议管理员通过本地安全策略配置账户锁定阈值（如 5 次无效登录后锁定）以缓解风险。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0582"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:40.593","remediation":"在「本地安全策略 → 账户策略 → 账户锁定策略」中，将账户锁定阈值设为 3 至 5 次无效登录，账户锁定时间设为 15 分钟以上（或设为\"直到管理员解锁\"），并将\"重置账户锁定计数器\"设为 15 分钟。域环境通过组策略（gpedit.msc / 域 GPO）统一下发，最后运行 gpupdate /force 刷新策略并复核生效。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0582","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0582.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/770e8f09ce14e637a09c7c619e10772aa6172bea/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0582.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0582","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/12e9f9121122940a38e93216069cda4e01d5b051/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0582.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0582.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/2a2be81fd4b47dc35d815a995b6429bd116a3b84/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5mrm-hq33-j44r/GHSA-5mrm-hq33-j44r.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0582.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86245/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154300_154400.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0849.toml"}]